EventListenerManager - Klasse in net.chaossquad.mclib.dynamicevents
Dynamically manages event listeners.
Instead of directly registering event listeners to Bukkit, listeners are registered to a ListenerOwner.
The ListenerManager then keeps the listeners registered as long as the ListenerOwner provides them.
If not, they are unregistered.
Listeners which should not be managed by this manager has to be excepted.
EventListenerManager(Plugin) - Konstruktor für Klasse net.chaossquad.mclib.dynamicevents.EventListenerManager
Creates a new EventListenerManager.

ExtendedListenerOwnerSource - Schnittstelle in net.chaossquad.mclib.dynamicevents
An ExtendedListenerOwnerSource is a ListenerOwnerSource with the difference that it can provide multiple listener owners.
